COMMAND>_ mini course


This course will be focused in an introduccion to COMMAND>, the basics concepts to build a compendia and practical sessions to work with COMMAND>.


What is COMMAND>_ ?

“COMMAND>_ is a web-based application used to download, collect and manage gene expression data from public databases.”
